a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Un manejador de eventos para errores en scripts en tiempo de ejecución.</p>\n\n<p>Note that some/many <code>error</code> events do not trigger <code>window.onerror</code>, you have to listen for them specifically.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">window.onerror = funcRef;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code>&nbsp;es una referencia a una función. Cuando la función devuelva&nbsp;<code>true</code>, se prevendrá el disparado del manejador de eventos por defecto. Parámetros de la función:\n\n  <ul>\n   <li>Mensaje de error (string)</li>\n   <li>Url en la que el error fue lanzado&nbsp;(string)</li>\n   <li>Número de línea en la que el error fue lanzado&nbsp;(number)</li>\n   <li>Dentro de la línea en la que el error ocurrió, número de columna correspondiente (number) </li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error\">Error Object</a> (object) </li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Example 1:</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Prevent error dialogs from displaying -which is the window's normal</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// behavior- by overriding the default event handler for error events that</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// go to the window.</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onerror <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Example 2:</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> gOldOnError <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onerror<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Override previous handler.</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onerror</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">myErrorHandler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">errorMsg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> url<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lineNumber</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gOldOnError<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Call previous handler.</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">gOldOnError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>errorMsg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> url<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lineNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Just let default handler run.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>El evento de error es lanzado cuando ocurre un error en el script.</p>\n\n<p>Cuando se use el marcado html en línea (<span class=\"nowiki\">&lt;body onerror=\"alert('an error occurred')&gt;...</span>), los argumentos son anónimos. Pueden ser referenciados usando desde&nbsp;<code>arguments[0]</code>&nbsp;hasta&nbsp;<code>arguments[2]</code>.</p>\n\n<p>No hay llamante&nbsp;<code><a class=\"external\" href=\"/en-US/Components.stack\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/En/Components.stack\">Components.stack</a>.caller</code>&nbsp;que recuperar. (Vea&nbsp;<a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=355430\" rel=\" noopener\"><strong>bug&nbsp;355430</strong></a>.)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificación","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://devedge-temp.mozilla.org/library/manuals/2000/javascript/1.3/reference/handlers.html#1120097\" rel=\" noopener\">JavaScript 1.1</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"example"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notes"},{"text":"Especificación","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Un manejador de eventos para errores en scripts en tiempo de ejecución.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onerror","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onerror/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onerror - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}